11 March 2014Members of the media are invited to a post State of Nation Address (SoNA) media briefing on Justice, Crime Prevention and Security (JCPS). Minister of Justice and Constitutional Development, Jeff Radebe will lead the media briefing. Details are as follows: Date: Wednesday, 12 March 2014 Time: 12h00 Venue: Imbizo Media Centre, Cape Town, Parliament NB: There will be a video-link to GCIS media briefing room, Tshedimosetso House, 1035 Francis Baard, Corner Festival Street, Hatfield, Pretoria RSVP: Ireen Magwai (Pretoria) Cell: 072 822 5869 E-mail:ireen@gcis.gov.za Mzimasi Ngqelu (Cape Town) Cell: 076 904 3557 E-mail: mzi@gcis.gov.za Enquiries: Nikelwa Tengimfene: 082 574 5495 Issued by Government Communication and Information System (GCIS)